extraDescription: Canadian Forces College (CFC) requires seven (7) resources at the Intermediate Level to act as facilitators for the Canadian Security Studies Programme (CSSP) 17 that runs from 28 September 2015 to 9 October 2015 at CFC in Toronto.
comments: This item was not reported previously. This contract was competitively sourced. This contract is a call-up against a Public Works and Government Services procurement tool.
